# Theseus user-guide screenshots

This directory holds PNG screenshots referenced by the LaTeX guides under
`docs/guides/`. Screenshots are produced by the Playwright capture pass
that prompt 65 wired up. Until a screenshot exists, the guide either
references it inside a `\IfFileExists{...}` block (so the build does not
fail) or omits the figure entirely.

Naming convention: `<guide-number>_<short-slug>.png`, e.g.
`01_quick_start_upload.png`.
